# Best Practices in Prompt Engineering

- Be clear and explicit in your instructions.  
- Use examples for complex tasks.  
- Break down multi-step tasks (scaffold).  
- Use delimiters to avoid ambiguity.  
- Iterate and test prompts regularly.  
- Avoid leading the AI to biased answers.  
- Combine Chain-of-Thought for reasoning tasks.  
- Use roleplay to set tone and style.  
- Prefer structured output for API integration.

---

Keep learning and experimenting!
